OL,3,CTourist tax: Growing number of
OL,4,Csurcharges in the UK and abroad
OL,6,FIf you've been away this summer, you
OL,7,Fmay have been hit with an unexpected
OL,8,Ftourist tax on check-out. They are on
OL,9,Fthe rise, here in the UK and abroad.
OL,10,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FWords by ITV News Consumer Producer
OL,14,FRachael Allison.
OL,16,FIt is known by many names: a tourist
OL,17,Flevy, visitor surcharge, or simply a
OL,18,Ftourist tax.
