OL,6,FWhatever the term, summer getaways are
OL,7,Fbecoming more expensive as travellers
OL,8,Facross Europe and beyond are
OL,9,Fincreasingly required to pay extra for
OL,10,Fovernight stays.
OL,12,FThe fees, typically added to hotel
OL,13,Fbills per adult per night, can quickly
OL,14,Fadd up - particularly for families or
OL,15,Fthose staying longer.
OL,17,FMallorca introduced its Sustainable
OL,18,FTourism Tax in 2016, sparking debate
OL,19,Famong visitors and residents alike.
