OL,6,FFor the Wilson family from
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough, the charge came as a
OL,8,Fshock.
OL,10,F"We normally would go to mainland
OL,11,FSpain," Christopher Wilson explained.
OL,13,F"Where we don't pay any tax, so yeah,
OL,14,Fit's kind of putting us off maybe
OL,15,Fcoming to the islands going forward.
OL,16,FWe paid enough money coming over here,
OL,17,Fso we shouldn't have to pay more tax."
OL,19,FFor families staying a fortnight, the
OL,20,Fextra cost can exceed E100 (#86)
OL,21,Fbefore the holiday has even begun.
