OL,6,FEnvironmental campaigners argue the
OL,7,Flevy is necessary. Sandy Hemingway
OL,8,Ffrom Friends of the Earth supports
OL,9,FMallorca's tax, pointing to the
OL,10,Fpressures of over-tourism.
OL,12,F"There are many signs of over-tourism,
OL,13,Fone of the very obvious ones is the
OL,14,Ftraffic. Our roads are just not built
OL,15,Ffor so many cars. But also, the
OL,16,Fbeautiful best places in the summer
OL,17,Ftime are just so full, it's almost
OL,18,Fimpossible to enjoy them."
OL,20,FThe UK is now preparing to follow suit.
