OL,6,FEdinburgh will introduce its visitor
OL,7,Flevy in 2026, though accommodation
OL,8,Fproviders will begin collecting it for
OL,9,Fbookings made on or after October 1,
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FEdinburgh Council Leader Jane Meagher
OL,13,Ftold ITV News that around #5 million
OL,14,Fraised will go towards housing and
OL,15,Fmanaging the impact of tourism.
