OL,6,F"The cost of accommodation in the city
OL,7,Fcentre puts working in the city centre
OL,8,Fbeyond the reach of many hospitality
OL,9,Fworkers. That's why it's absolutely
OL,10,Freasonable and consistent with the
OL,11,Flegislation for us to use some of this
OL,12,Fmoney."
OL,14,FOther UK cities are already charging
OL,15,Fvisitors. Manchester and Liverpool
OL,16,Fboth apply a nightly levy`#1 and #2
OL,17,Frespectively.
