OL,6,FIn Liverpool, the scheme is run by the
OL,7,FLiverpool Accommodation BID, which
OL,8,Freinvests the money into improving the
OL,9,Fcity and promoting its visitor economy.
OL,11,FBill Addy, CEO of Liverpool
OL,12,FAccommodation BID, said: "The main
OL,13,Fbenefit is that we can sell our city
OL,14,Finto the world. We're an iconic
OL,15,Finternational city, but we need to be
OL,16,Fable to promote ourselves and we are
OL,17,Fable to do that."
OL,19,FDespite grumbles from holidaymakers,
OL,20,Fevidence suggests tourism taxes are
OL,21,Frarely a deterrent.
